      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">3</infon>
        <offset>295</offset>
        <text>This so-called 'opal paradox' is generally attributed to a higher efficiency of opal preservation in the Southern Ocean than elsewhere.
</text>
        <annotation id="T5">
          <infon key="brat-id">T5</infon>
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <location length="53" offset="361"/>
          <text>efficiency of opal preservation in the Southern Ocean</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T6">
          <infon key="brat-id">T6</infon>
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
