          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <node refid="T6" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T5" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">4</infon>
        <offset>431</offset>
        <text>Here we report biogenic silica production rates, opal rain rates in the water column and opal sediment burial rates for the Indian Ocean sector of the Southern Ocean, which show that the assumed opal paradox is a result of underestimated opal production rates and overestimated opal accumulation rates.
</text>
        <annotation id="T7">
          <infon key="brat-id">T7</infon>
