          <node refid="T13" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>941</offset>
        <text>The comparison of our revised opal preservation efficiencies for the Southern Ocean with existing values from the equatorial Pacific Ocean and the North Atlantic Ocean shows that spatial differences in preservation efficiencies are not the primary reason for the differences in sedimentary opal accumulation.
</text>
        <annotation id="T15">
          <infon key="brat-id">T15</infon>
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
