          <text>accumulation</text>
        </annotation>
        <relation id="E8">
          <infon key="brat-id">E8</infon>
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <node refid="T16" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T15" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>1250</offset>
        <text>The reconciliation of surface production rates and sedimentary accumulation rates may enable the use of biogenic opal in the reconstruction of palaeoproductivity when the factors that affect the Si/C ratio are better understood.
</text>
      </sentence>
